{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"17081","heading":"Commercial high-performance green buildings","label":"17081 Commercial high-performance green buildings","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17081","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/ch152/schIII/ptB","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs17081","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","Effective DateSection effective on the date that is 1 day after , see , set out as a note under , The Congress.Dec. 19, 2007section 1601 of Pub. L. 110–140section 1824 of Title 2","Executive Documents","Change of NameOffice of the Federal Environmental Executive reestablished as the Office of the Chief Sustainability Officer by Ex. Ord. No. 13693, § 6, , 80 F.R. 15877, formerly set out in a note under .Mar. 19, 2015section 4321 of this title"],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"Director of Commercial High-Performance Green Buildings","label":"a Director of Commercial High-Performance Green Buildings","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17081/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17081","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs17081%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17081/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17081/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs17081%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"establish and manage the Office of Commercial High-Performance Green Buildings; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17081/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17081/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs17081%2Fa%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"carry out other duties as required under this part.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Qualifications","label":"b Qualifications","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17081/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17081","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs17081%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Commercial Director shall be an individual, who by reason of professional background and experience, is specifically qualified to carry out the duties required under this part.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"c","heading":"Duties","label":"c Duties","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17081/c","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17081","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs17081%2Fc","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17081/c/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17081/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs17081%2Fc%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"coordinate the activities of the Office of Commercial High-Performance Green Buildings with the activities of the Office of Federal High-Performance Green Buildings;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17081/c/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17081/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs17081%2Fc%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"develop the legal predicates and agreements for, negotiate, and establish one or more public-private partnerships with the Consortium, members of the Consortium, and other capable parties meeting the qualifications of the Consortium, to further such development;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17081/c/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17081/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs17081%2Fc%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"represent the public and the Department in negotiating and performing in accord with such public-private partnerships;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"4","heading":null,"label":"4","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17081/c/4","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17081/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs17081%2Fc%2F4","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"use appropriated funds in an effective manner to encourage the maximum investment of private funds to achieve such development;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"5","heading":null,"label":"5","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17081/c/5","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17081/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs17081%2Fc%2F5","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"promote research and development of high-performance green buildings, consistent with ; andsection 17083 of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"6","heading":null,"label":"6","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17081/c/6","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17081/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs17081%2Fc%2F6","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendm