xt":"summarizes and highlights development, at the State and local level, of high-performance green building initiatives, including executive orders, policies, or laws adopted promoting high-performance green building (including the status of implementation of those initiatives).","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]}
